n of the data expected from on-going experiments, the SNR\nproduction/acceleration of secondary nuclei should be considered, if any, to\nprevent a possible mis-determination of the CR transport parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Mar 2012 21:48:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 22 Jul 2012 10:18:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-07-24"}
