pical coronal conditions, such\nblobs may also carry an energy flux of 7.0$\\times10^{6}$ ergs cm$^{-2}$\ns$^{-1}$ to re-balance the coronal losses above active regions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Mar 2012 09:57:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
